long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Garbage is an HTML5 action puzzle game where players throw items into a trash can by swiping in different directions.
Garbage is a fun and challenging HTML5 game that tests players' coordination and reflexes. In the game, players give control of a character. They must use it to throw various items into a trash can by swiping in different directions. The items will appear on the screen. And move toward the character, and players must swipe in the correct path to throw them into the trash can.
The game's objective is to throw as many items into the trash can as possible. As players progress through the game, the number, and speed of the objects increase. Making it more challenging to keep up. To succeed, players must have quick reflexes and be able to anticipate the items' movements.
One of the unique features of Garbage is its intuitive and easy-to-use controls. Players can throw the items simply by swiping their fingers in the desired direction.
Its challenging gameplay, various game modes, and easy-to-use controls make it a must-play for anyone looking for a brain-teasing and engaging game.
